<section id="philosophy" class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-32 flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl tracking-tight leading-none text-foreground">
            PHILOSOPHY<br>BEHIND MY WORK
        </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="group relative flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-black border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-black/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">1</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold">Visual Aesthetics</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed">
                I believe that a product's visual appeal is just as important as its functionality. 
                Striking visuals create a lasting impression and build trust with the user.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="group relative flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-black border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-black/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">2</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold">User Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Design is not just about how it looks, but how it works. 
                I focus on creating intuitive, seamless, and enjoyable experiences for every user.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="group relative flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-black border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-black/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-colors duration-300">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">3</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold">Performance</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Speed is a feature. I optimize every line of code to ensure lightning-fast load times and smooth interactions across all devices.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="group relative flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-black border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-black/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-colors duration-300">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">4</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Pushing boundaries with new technologies and creative solutions. 
                I love to experiment and bring fresh ideas to life on the web.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
